(26, 'Unit Pendukung', 'Supporting Unit', '<h2 style="border-bottom: 2px solid #CCCCCC;"><img src="images/folder_32.png" alt="" width="25" height="25" /><a href="#"> Unit Pendukung </a></h2>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">KLINIK TANAMAN</span></strong></p>\n<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Klinik tanaman adalah bagian dari unit departemen untuk pelayanan masyarakat dengan fungsi utama : (1) penyuluhan teknologi PHT kepada petani dan institusi terkait; (2) sebagai media bagi staf dan mahasiswa guna pengalaman dalam menangani berbagai masalah nyata hama dan penyakit; (3) sebagai mekanisme timbal balik mengetahui topik terpenting dan terkini dalam perlindungan tanaman.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;" align="center"><strong><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">PUSAT PENGENDALIAN HAMA TERPADU</span></strong></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Pusat untuk PHT adalah sebuah unit departemen yang mengatur pelatihan dan penelitian dalam teknologi pendukung PHT. Peserta Pusat untuk PHT yang berasal dari bermacam-macam institusi mempertunjukkan posisi strategis dalam pusat penyuluhan ilmu dan teknologi pendukung PHT.</span></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>ANALISA DATA DAN PUSAT INFORMASI HAMA DAN PENYAKIT</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Konsultasi desain eksperimen dan survei</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Analisa data dan bangun model</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Bangun data base hama dan penyakit tanaman</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Desain grafis</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Pelayanan dalam percobaan laboratorium mahasiswa</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>INSECT TEACHING COLLECTION</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Pelayanan dalam identifikasi serangga</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Sebagai sumber referensi serangga</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Sebagai fasilitas pembelajaran</span></li>\n<li style="margin-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Salah satu objek eduwisata IPB</span></li>\n<li style="margin-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Peningkatan dalam koleksi serangga</span></li>\n<li style="margin-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Membuat koleksi serangga untuk institusi lain</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;" align="center"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong><br /></strong></span></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><br /></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><br /></span></p>', '<h2 style="border-bottom: 2px solid #CCCCCC;"><img src="images/folder_32.png" alt="" width="25" height="25" /><a href="#"> Supporting Unit </a></h2>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;" align="center"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>PLANT CLINIC</strong></span></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Plant clinic is a part of departmental unit for community services with main functions : (1) dissemination of IPM technology to farmers and related institutions; (2) as a media for staff and students to experience in handling the real pest and disease problems; (3) as a feedback mechanism to figure out the most important and recent topics in plant protection.</span><strong></strong></p>\n<p align="center"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong><br /></strong></span></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;" align="center"><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><strong>CENTER FOR INTEGRATED PEST MANAGEMENT</strong> <br /></span></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Center for IPM is a unit of the department that organizes training and research on IPM-supported technologies.&nbsp; Participants of Center for IPM come from various institutions showing the strategic position of the center in disseminating IPM-supporting sciences and technology.</span></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">DATA ANALYSIS AND INFORMATION CENTER OF PLANT AND DISEASES</span></strong></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Data Analysis and Information Center conducts proffesional service activities such as :</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li style="margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Experimental and survey design consultancy</span></li>\n<li style="margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Data analysis and model building</span></li>\n<li style="margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Plant pest and disease data base building</span></li>\n<li style="margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Graphic design</span></li>\n<li style="margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Serving in student laboratory exercise</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;" align="center"><strong><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">INSECT TEACHING COLLECTION</span></strong></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Departmental insect museum also known as Insect Teaching Collection (ITC)&nbsp; housed insect collection to support teaching-learning , and research activities.&nbsp;&nbsp; ITC also serves program for insect identification and it is a part of universities edutourism</span></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><br /></span></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><br /></span></p>', '2011-08-18 10:29:03', 1);
