(25, 'Tentang Departemen', 'About Department', '<h2 style="border-bottom: 2px solid #CCCCCC;"><img src="images/news.jpg" alt="" width="25" height="25" /><a href="#"> Tentang Departemen</a></h2>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Sejarah departemen ini diawali pada 1950 sebagai divisi Entomologi-Fitopatologi, Fakultas Pertanian, Universitas Indonesia. Pada 1972, namanya berubah menjadi Departemen Ilmu Hama dan Penyakit Tanaman sebagai bagian dari Fakultas Pertanian, Institut Pertanian Bogor. Departemen ini kembali berganti nama menjadi Departemen Proteksi Tanaman pada 2005.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Pada awalnya, Departemen ini hanya menyediakan program strata satu (S1) dan pada 1976, meresmikan program pasca sarjana untuk gelar master dalam Patologi dan Entomologi Tanaman yang diikuti program Doktor pada 1978.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Program Sarjana menjadi lebih kuat ketika Departemen ini memperoleh hibah melalui Kualitas untuk Pendidikan Sarjana (2000 - 2003); begitu pula dengan program pasca sarjana yang memperoleh hibah melalui Proyek URGE &nbsp;(1997 - 2000). Program studi sarjana memperoleh akreditasi A dari&nbsp; Badan Akreditasi Nasional sejak 1988 hingga 2012. Kinerja Departemen ini diringankan dengan adanya program hibah kompetitif B dari DIKTI (2005 &ndash; 2007).</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Departemen Proteksi Tanaman telah dikenal sejak lama dalam memainkan peranan penting, dan sebagai agen perubahan, serta mentransfer teknologi dalam pengembangan berbagai strategi pengendalian hama dan penyakit tanaman.&nbsp; Dengan sumber daya manusia yang begitu hebat, berbagai fasilitas serta prestasi di bidang pendidikan, penelitian, dan layanan masyarakat, Departemen ini selalu&nbsp; meningkatkan keteguhannya untuk berkontribusi dalam kebutuhan bangsa.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<h2 style="border-bottom: 2px solid #CCCCCC;"><img src="images/news.jpg" alt="" width="25" height="25" /><a href="#"> &nbsp;About Departement</a></h2>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; The Department&rsquo;s history started in 1950 as a division of Entomology-Phytopathology, Faculty of &nbsp;&nbsp;Agriculture, University of Indonesia.&nbsp; In 1972, the name changed into the Department of Plant Pest and Disease as a part of Faculty of Agriculture, Bogor Agricultural University.&nbsp; Department&rsquo;s name was altered to Department of Plant Protection in 2005.</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; In the beginning, the Department catered only undergraduate program (S1) and in 1976 the Department initiated graduate program for Master degree in Plant Pathology and Entomology followed by Doctoral program in 1978.</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; The undergraduate program became stronger when the Department received a grant through Quality for Under graduate Education (2000 &ndash; 2003); similarly with the graduate program with a grant through URGE Project (1997 - 2000).&nbsp; Undergraduate study program received grade A accreditation from&nbsp; National Accreditation Agency since 1988 which valid until 2012.&nbsp; Performance of the Department was alleviated through Program B competitive grant from Directorate General of Higher Education (2005 &ndash; 2007).</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Linkages to international communities, private industries, other scientific institutions and NGO&rsquo;s have long been established.&nbsp; These collaboration showed the outstanding performance of the Department.</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; The Department of Plant Protection has been recognized to play a significant role and serve as an agent of change and transfer of technology in the development of pests and diseases management strategies.&nbsp; With excellence human resources, facilities as well as achievement in education, research, and community services, the Department is always advance its courage to contribute to the need of the nation.</span></p>', '2011-08-18 10:31:15', 1),
(27, 'Laboratorium Penelitian', 'Research Laboratory', '<h2 style="border-bottom: 2px solid #CCCCCC;"><img src="images/news.jpg" alt="" width="25" height="25" /><a href="#"> &nbsp;Laboratorium</a></h2>\n<h3 style="font-family: arial; color: black;">&nbsp;</h3>\n<h3 style="font-family: arial; color: black;">Laboratorium Riset</h3>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<center><img src="images/research lab.jpg" alt="research lab" width="400" height="300" /></center>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; color: black;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Berbagai laboratorium Penelitian terdiri atas 6 laboratorium entomologi/rodentologi dan 5 laboratorium patologi tumbuhan. Peralatan modern dan maju tersedia guna mendukung berbagai aktivitas penelitian</span></p>\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; color: black;" align="justify">&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; color: black; margin-left: 30px;"><a href="page/section/10">Laboratorium Sistematik Serangga</a></li>\n<li style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; color: black; margin-left: 30px;"><a href="page/section/11">Laboratorium Bionomi Serangga dan Lingkungan</a></li>\n<li style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; color: black; margin-left: 30px;"><a href="page/section/12">Insect Physiology and Toxicology Laboratory</a></li>\n<li style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; color: black; margin-left: 30px;"><a href="page/section/16">Laboratorium Pengendalian Hayati</a></li>\n<li style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; color: black; margin-left: 30px;"><a href="page/section/17">Laboratorium Patologi Serangga</a></li>\n<li style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; color: black; margin-left: 30px;"><a href="page/section/18">Laboratorium Vertebrata Hama</a></li>\n<li style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; color: black; margin-left: 30px;"><a href="page/section/19">Laboratorium Mikologi</a></li>\n<li style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; color: black; margin-left: 30px;"><a href="page/section/20">Laboratorium Bakteriologi Tumbuhan</a></li>\n<li style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; color: black; margin-left: 30px;"><a href="page/section/21">Laboratorium Bakteriologi Tumbuhan</a></li>\n</ul>', '<h2 style="border-bottom: 2px solid #CCCCCC;"><img src="images/news.jpg" alt="" width="25" height="25" /><a href="#"> &nbsp;Laboratory</a></h2>\n<h3 style="font-family: arial; color: black;">&nbsp;</h3>\n<h3 style="font-family: arial; color: black;">Research Laboratory</h3>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<center><img src="images/research lab.jpg" alt="research lab" width="400" height="300" /></center>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; color: black;" align="justify">Research laboratories are composed of 5 entomology, 1 rodentology and 5 plant pathology laboratories. Modern and advanced equipments are available to support research activities. The laboratories consist of&nbsp; :</p>\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; color: black;" align="justify">&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; color: black; margin-left: 30px;"><a href="page/section/10">Insect Biosystematic Laboratory</a></li>\n<li style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; color: black; margin-left: 30px;"><a href="page/section/11">Insect Bionomy and Ecology Laboratory</a></li>\n<li style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; color: black; margin-left: 30px;"><a href="page/section/12">Insect Physiology and Toxicology Laboratory</a></li>\n<li style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; color: black; margin-left: 30px;"><a href="page/section/16">Biological Control Laboratory</a></li>\n<li style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; color: black; margin-left: 30px;"><a href="page/section/17">Insect Pathology Laboratory</a></li>\n<li style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; color: black; margin-left: 30px;"><a href="page/section/18">Vertebrate Pests Laboratory</a></li>\n<li style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; color: black; margin-left: 30px;"><a href="page/section/19">Plant Micology Laboratory</a></li>\n<li style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; color: black; margin-left: 30px;"><a href="page/section/20">Plant Bacteriology Laboratory</a></li>\n<li style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; color: black; margin-left: 30px;"><a href="page/section/21">Plant Virology Laboratory</a></li>\n</ul>', '2011-08-18 09:42:41', 5),
(28, 'Fokus Riset', 'Research Focus', '<h2 style="border-bottom: 2px solid #CCCCCC;"><img src="images/news.jpg" alt="" width="25" height="25" /><a href="#"> &nbsp;Fokus Riset</a></h2>\n<h4>&nbsp;</h4>\n<p style="text-align: left;" align="center"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>LABORATORIUM BIOSISTEMATIK SERANGGA</strong></span></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>Minat Penelitian</strong><strong>:</strong><strong></strong></span></p>\n<ol>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Bio-sistematik dan biodeversitas serangga</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Bio-ekologi dan biodeversitas parasitoid</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Bio-ekologi skala serangga dan kutu tepung</span></li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;" align="center"><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><strong>LABORATORIUM BIONOMI DAN EKOLOGI SERANGGA</strong><strong></strong></span></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><strong>Minat Penelitian</strong><strong>:</strong><strong></strong></span></p>\n<ol>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Bio-ekologi serangga hama dan pengembangan strategi pengendalian hama terpadu (PHT)</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Biologis, ekologis dan strategi pengendalian hama gudang.</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Interaksi tanaman-serangga dan serangga-parasitoid</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Analisa ekonomi pertanian dengan menekankan pada kesejahteraan masyarakat, kebijakan pemerintah, lingkungan, ekonometrik, dan statistika terapan</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Pengendalian tungau dan musuh alaminya.</span></li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;" align="center"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>LABORATORIUM FISIOLOGI DAN TOKSIKOLOGI SERANGGA</strong><strong> </strong><strong></strong></span></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>Research</strong><strong> </strong><strong>Interest:</strong></span></p>\n<ol>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Eksplorasi pemanfaatan tanaman potensial sebagai insektisida tumbuhan</span><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">.</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Interaksi tanaman-serangga, inang-parasitoid, dan mangsa-predator</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Evaluasi dan efisiensi insektisida untuk hama dan musuh alaminya</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Pengembangan bio-intensif perlindungan tanaman</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Fisiologi serangga.</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Pengembangan makanan semi-sintetik dalam pembesaran masal parasitoid dan predator</span></li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;" align="center"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>LABORATORIUM PENGENDALIAN HAYATI</strong><strong> </strong><strong></strong></span></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>Minat Penelitian</strong><strong>:</strong><strong></strong></span></p>\n<ol>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Interaksi inang-parasitoid</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Korelasi struktur lanskap pertanian dan biodeversitas serangga</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Pengendalian hayati serangga hama</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Bio-ekologi parasitoid dan predator</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Pengembangan strategi PHT untuk pertanian organik</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Interkasi inang-parasitoid dan fisiologi dan tingkah laku serangga</span></li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;" align="center"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>LABORATORIUM PATOLOGI SERANGGA</strong><strong> </strong><strong></strong></span></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>Minat Penelitian</strong><strong>:</strong><strong></strong></span></p>\n<ol>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Patologi serangga dan pemanfaatan patogen serangga dalam pengendalian hama</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Cendawan entomopatogen dan interaksi cendawan entomoptoralean-inang</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Epidemiologi (epizoologi), karakterisasi biologis dan fisis, simptomatologi (histo-sytopatologi)</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Genetik molekuler ascovirus pada larva lepidoptera</span></li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;" align="center"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>LABORATORIUM VERTEBRATA HAMA</strong></span></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>Minat Penelitian</strong><strong>:</strong></span></p>\n<ol>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Studi bio-ekologi tikus dan vertebrata hama</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Pengembangan strategi pengendalian tikus dan vertebrata hama</span></li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;" align="center"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>LABORATORIUM MIKOLOGI TUMBUHAN</strong></span></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>Minat Penelitian</strong><strong>:</strong></span></p>\n<ol>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Pengendalian hayati penyakit tanaman</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Epidemiologi penyakit tanaman</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Ekologi dan pengendalian hayati patogen tular benih</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Ekstrak kompos untuk pengendalian penyakit</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Pengendalian cendawan tular tanah berbasis ekologis</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Interaksi cendawan patogenik dan agen pengendalian hayati</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Strategi untuk penyaringan agen pengendalian hayati</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Formulasi agen pengendalian hayati</span></li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;" align="center"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>LABORATORIUM BAKTERIOLOGI TUMBUHAN</strong></span></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>Minat penelitian</strong><strong>:</strong></span></p>\n<ol>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Pengembangan teknik pengendalian penyakit kudis umum pada kentang</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Produksi massal agen pengendalian hayati</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Penyaringan dan karakterisasi molekuler pemroduksian bakteri kitinase</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Karakterisasi penyakit busuk lunak pepaya</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Identifikasi penyakit getah kuning pada manggis</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Karakterisasi molekuler penyakit darah bakteri pada pisang</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Pengembangan varietas lada resisten terhadap <em>Ralstonia solanacearum</em>.</span></li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;" align="center"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>LABORATORIUM VIROLOGI TUMBUHAN</strong></span></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>Minat Penelitian</strong><strong>:</strong></span></p>\n<ol>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Mikroskop elektron dalam fitopatologi</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Biologi molekuler virus tumbuhan: deteksi, karakterisasi, variasi, dan interaksi virus tumbuhan dalam induksi penyakit</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Pengembangan metode deteksi molekuler patogen tanaman</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Studi pada hubungan serangga (vektor)-penyakit tanaman</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Studi pada diversitas genetik virus tumbuhan</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Pengembangan tanaman resisten transgenik terhadap patogen</span></li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;" align="center"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>LABORATORIUM NEMATODA TUMBUHAN</strong><strong> </strong><strong></strong></span></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>Minat Penelitian</strong><strong>:</strong></span></p>\n<ol>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Bio-ekologi nematoda parasit tumbuhan</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Pengendalian agroiekosistem tanaman setahun</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Pembesaran massal nematoda pada akar/kultur jaringan</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Interaksi tumbuhan-nematoda dan pengendalian nematoda pada tanaman dan tumbuhan lanskap</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Interaksi penyakit pada pengembangan penyakit kompleks tumbuhan</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Interaksi nematoda dan patogen tular tanah</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Rhizosfer dan bakteri endofit dan aktivitas biologisnya &nbsp;pada penyakit tular tanah</span></li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<h2 style="border-bottom: 2px solid #CCCCCC;"><img src="images/news.jpg" alt="" width="25" height="25" /><a href="#"> &nbsp;Research Focus</a></h2>\n<h4>&nbsp;<strong></strong></h4>\n<h4>&nbsp;</h4>\n<h4><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><strong>INSECT BIOSYSTEMATICS</strong><strong> LABORATORY</strong></span><strong></strong> </span></h4>\n<h4><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-size: small;">Research Interest:</span></strong></span></h4>\n<ol>\n<li style="margin-left: 60px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Insect bio-systematic and biodiversity</span></li>\n<li style="margin-left: 60px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Bio-ecology and biodiversity of parasitoids </span></li>\n<li style="margin-left: 60px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Bio-ecology of scale insect and mealybugs</span><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"> <br /></span></li>\n</ol>\n<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;" align="right"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>INSECT BIONOMY AND ECOLOGY</strong><strong> </strong><strong>LABORATORY </strong><strong></strong></span></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>Research</strong><strong> </strong><strong>Interest:</strong><strong></strong></span></p>\n<ol>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong></strong>Bio-ecology of insect pests and development of integrated pest management (IPM) strategy </span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Biological, ecological and control strategy of stored-product&nbsp; pests</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Plant-insect and insect-parasitoid interaction</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Economic analysis of pest management strategy </span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Management of mites and their natural enemies&nbsp; <br /></span></li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;" align="center"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>INSECT PHYSIOLOGY AND TOXICOLOGY LABORATORY&nbsp; </strong></span></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>Research</strong><strong> </strong><strong>Interest:</strong></span></p>\n<ol>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong></strong>Exploration of plant potentially used as botanical insecticides</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Plant-insect interaction, host-parasitoid and prey-predator interaction</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Evaluation and efficacy of insecticide for pests and their natural enemies</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Development of bio-intensive plant protection</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Insect physiology</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Development of semi-synthetic diet in mass rearing of parasitoids&nbsp; and predators <br /></span></li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;" align="center"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>BIOLOGICAL CONTROL</strong><strong> </strong><strong>LABORATORY&nbsp; </strong></span></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>Research</strong><strong> </strong><strong>Interest:</strong><strong></strong></span></p>\n<ol>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Host-parasitoid interaction</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Correlation of agricultural landscape structure and insect biodiversity</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Biological control of insect pests</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Bio-ecology of parasitoids and predators</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Development of IPM strategy for organic farming</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Host-parasitoid interaction and insect physiology and behaviors</span></li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;" align="center"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>INSECT PATHOLOGY</strong><strong> </strong><strong>LABORATORY </strong><strong></strong></span></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>Research</strong><strong> </strong><strong>Interest:</strong><strong></strong></span></p>\n<ol>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Insect Pathology and the use of insect pathogens in pest control</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Entomopathogenic fungi and entomophthoralean fungi-host &nbsp;interaction</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Epidemiology (epizootiology), biological and physical characterization, symptomatology (hysto-cytopathology)</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Molecular genetic of ascovirus on lepidopterous larvae</span></li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;" align="center"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>VERTEBRATE PESTS</strong><strong> </strong><strong>LABORATORY</strong></span></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>Research</strong><strong> </strong><strong>Interest:</strong></span></p>\n<ol>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Study of bio-ecology rat and vertebrate pests </span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Development of control strategy of rat and vertebrate pests</span></li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;" align="center"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>PLANT MYCOLOGY</strong><strong> </strong><strong>LABORATORY</strong></span></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>Research</strong><strong> </strong><strong>Interest:</strong><strong> </strong></span></p>\n<ol>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Biological control of plant diseases</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Plant disease epidemiology</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Ecology and biological control of seed-borne pathogens</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Compost extract for disease control</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Ecologically based management of soil-borne fungi </span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Interaction of pathogenic fungi and biological control agents</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Strategies for screening biological control agents</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Formulation of biological control agents&nbsp; <br /></span></li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;" align="center"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>PLANT BACTERIOLOGY</strong><strong> </strong><strong>LABORATORY </strong><strong></strong></span></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>Research</strong><strong> </strong><strong>Interest:</strong></span></p>\n<ol>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong></strong>Development of control techniques of common scab diseases on&nbsp; potato</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Mass production of&nbsp; biocontrol agents</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Screening and molecular characterization of producing-chitinase bacteria</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Characterization of soft rot diseases of papaya</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Identification of yellow gum diseases on mangosteen</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Molecular characterization of&nbsp; blood diseases bacterium on banana</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Development of&nbsp; pepper resistance varieties to <em>Ralstonia solanacearum</em>.</span></li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;" align="center"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>PLANT VIROLOGY</strong><strong> </strong><strong>LABORATORY </strong><strong></strong></span></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>Research</strong><strong> </strong><strong>Interest:</strong><strong></strong></span></p>\n<ol>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong></strong>Electron microscope in phytopathology</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Molecular biology of plant viruses: detection, <em>characterization, variation </em>&nbsp;and interaction of plant viruses in disease induction</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Development of molecular detection methods of plant pathogens</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Study on insects (vector)-plant diseases relationship</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Study on genetic diversity of plant viruses</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Development of transgenic plants resistant to pathogens</span></li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;" align="center"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>PLANT NAMATODES</strong><strong> </strong><strong>LABORATORY </strong><strong></strong></span></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"><strong>Research</strong><strong> </strong><strong>Interest:</strong><strong> </strong></span></p>\n<ol>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Bio-ecology of plant parasitic nematodes</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Management of agro-ecosystem of annual crops</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Mass rearing of nematodes in roots/tissue culture</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Plant-nematode interaction and management of nematodes in crops and plant landscapes</span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Diseases interaction in development of plant diseases complex </span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Interaction of nematodes and soil-borne pathogens </span></li>\n<li style="text-align: left; margin-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Rhyzosphere and endophytic bacteria and their biological&nbsp;&nbsp; activities on soil-borne diseases</span><strong> </strong></li>\n</ol>', '2011-08-18 10:20:15', 1);
